strings: <voice_0x0100149D><center>You...fools...
<voice_0x0100149E><center>How many more times...

<voice_0x0100149F><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Your Holiness!
Are you hurt?

<voice_0x010014A0><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Thank the Goddess!
He still has a pulse.
What happened!?

<voice_0x010014A1><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Was it that hellhound?
What on earth is going on!?
<voice_0x010014A2><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Marcello!

<voice_0x010014A3><se_low>High Priest Rolo: What are you doing just standing there!?
Carry His Holiness to his bed at once!

<voice_0x010014A4><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Get a move on, you sluggard!
You're supposed to be master of the guard!
I'll have you demoted if you don't snap to it!

<voice_0x010014A6><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Are you deaf, Marcello!?
I just gave you an order!

<voice_0x010014A7><se_def>Marcello: Ah ha ha! Well, well, well, High Priest Rolo!
I had no idea you were so devious!

<voice_0x010014A8><se_low>High Priest Rolo: What are you laughing about?
I fail to see anything funny about the situation!
<voice_0x010014A9><se_def>Marcello: Enough of the pretence! I know it was you who employed these thugs and that dog...

<voice_0x010014AA><se_def>Marcello: What an elaborate scheme!
Engineering a diversion to give you time to effect the assassination of the Lord High Priest!
<voice_0x010014AB><se_def>Marcello: I was aware of your desire to be his successor, but to resort to murder...?

<voice_0x010014AC><se_low>High Priest Rolo: What rot! How dare you!?
I planned nothing of the sort!

<voice_0x010014AD><se_def>Marcello: Arrest them! Exile High Priest Rolo to
Purgatory Island along with these thugs!
They will learn that succession comes
at a high price! Take them away!
<voice_0x010014AE><se_low>*: Yessir!

<voice_0x010014B0><se_def>Marcello: They say that ‘every dog has its day’!
And it seems I have a dog to thank for mine!
<voice_0x010014B1><se_def>Marcello: ...Hm?

<voice_0x010014B2><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Insolent traitors!
How dare you treat me like this!?
I am to be the next Lord High Priest!

<voice_0x010014B3><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Do you hear me!?
I am innocent!
You should arrest that miscreant!

<voice_0x010014B4><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Stop! Wait!
This is all a misunderstanding!

<voice_0x010014B5><se_low>High Priest Rolo: One of my own men! That turncoat!
How could Marcello do this to me!?

<voice_0x010014B6><se_low>High Priest Rolo: I was so close! He was a frail old man.
All I had to do was wait, and I'd have become the next Lord High Priest for sure...

<voice_0x010014B8><se_low>High Priest Rolo: This is Purgatory Island.
Where our most heinous criminals
are locked away until they die.
<voice_0x010014B9><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Once you're in here, death is the only way out.

<voice_0x010014BA><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Curse Marcello!
That traitor will rot in hell!

<voice_0x010014BB><se_def>Marcello: The Lord High Priest dies from shock,
and the High Priest out of the picture too!
This is better than I ever could have hoped!
<voice_0x010014BC><se_def>Marcello: What the<endash> Urgh!

<voice_0x010014BD><se_def>Marcello: U-Urgh...! My head... I can't bear it!
What's happening...?

<voice_0x010014BE><center>My flesh and blood are trapped.
<center>Sealed away by those infernal sages...

<voice_0x010014BF><se_def>Marcello: That voice...
Who is it...?
What do you want!?
<voice_0x010014C0><se_def>Marcello: The sceptre...?

<voice_0x010014C1><center>A new hand to hold the sceptre!
<center>A new body to control!

<voice_0x010014C2><center>You are a slave to the sceptre!
<center>You will obey my command!
<voice_0x010014C3><se_def>Marcello: I...obey...no one!
<voice_0x010014C4><center>What!?
<voice_0x010014C5><se_def>Marcello: I'm notoriously bad at taking orders.
<voice_0x010014C6><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Marcello may be a traitor, but I could not ignore his uncommon determination and strength. Not to mention his skill with a sword.
<voice_0x010014C7><se_low>High Priest Rolo: It was my intention to use him to position myself as the Lord High Priest's successor.

<voice_0x010014C8><se_low>High Priest Rolo: I used Marcello to eliminate all opposition.
All I had to do was wait.
<voice_0x010014C9><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Once I had cleared the path for my promotion, the only obstacle was time.

<voice_0x010014CA><se_low>High Priest Rolo: But I did not foresee this turn of events.
How could I let that stripling undo me!?

<voice_0x010014CB><se_low>High Priest Rolo: Ah... Listen!
You can hear the voices of the convicts below.

<voice_0x010014CC><se_low>High Priest Rolo: We have arrived.
This is Purgatory Island.
Hell on earth!
